The paper deals with automated classification of sentiment in research citations, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. This falls under the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and deep learning (cs.DL).
